OL,3,C87-year-old with dementia left on care
OL,4,Chome floor for hour after fall
OL,6,FTwo care workers left an 87-year-old
OL,7,Fdementia sufferer on the floor of a
OL,8,Fcare home for nearly an hour after he
OL,9,Ffell, a court heard.
OL,11,FDianne Brown and Thitikan Khaengraeng
OL,12,Fdeliberately ignored the man's
OL,13,F"plight", repeatedly walking past him
OL,14,Fto prioritise other jobs, was told.
OL,16,FOther worried residents at Holyrood
OL,17,FHouse, in , tried to help him up.
