OL,3,C87-year-old with dementia left on care
OL,4,Chome floor for hour after fall
OL,6,FBrown was doing medication rounds and
OL,7,Fwalked past the room where the
OL,8,Fpensioner was lying on the floor.
OL,10,FShe said "Oh God", but did not attempt
OL,11,Fto help him.
OL,13,FShe asked another resident what she
OL,14,Fwas supposed to do if he kept falling
OL,15,Fand she said that she could not lift
OL,16,Fhim.
OL,18,FShe did not go back into the room to
OL,19,Fcheck on him.
