OL,3,C87-year-old with dementia left on care
OL,4,Chome floor for hour after fall
OL,6,FAnother resident in the hallway tried
OL,7,Fto persuade the pensioner to get
OL,8,Fhimself up.
OL,10,FSeventeen minutes after his fall, the
OL,11,Fman started to shuffle his way out of
OL,12,Fthe room.
OL,14,F"The resident present tried to assist
OL,15,Fhim, but could not," Miss Baines said.
OL,17,FKhaengraeng appeared in the corridor
OL,18,Fabout 23 minutes after the fall. She
OL,19,Fshut the door of the room he had
OL,20,F"dragged himself from" and left the
OL,21,Fhallway.
