OL,3,C87-year-old with dementia left on care
OL,4,Chome floor for hour after fall
OL,6,FKhaengraeng came into the hallway and
OL,7,Ftold the pensioner that she needed
OL,8,FBrown to help her. She went upstairs
OL,9,Fand other residents then tried to
OL,10,Fintervene.
OL,12,F"After a couple of minutes or so,
OL,13,FDianne Brown re-entered the hallway
OL,14,Fand told the residents not to lift
OL,15,Fhim," Miss Baines said.
OL,17,FBrown told him that, if he was going
OL,18,Fto crawl around, he would have to stay
OL,19,Fon the floor.
