OL,6,FThe two carers then lifted the
OL,7,Fpensioner from the floor and placed
OL,8,Fhim on the chair.
OL,10,F"This was at just before 9pm,
OL,11,Fapproximately 57 minutes after the
OL,12,Finitial fall," Miss Baines said.
OL,14,FThe incident came to light when the
OL,15,Fcare home manager came on shift the
OL,16,Fnext day and spotted the fall and its
OL,17,Faftermath on CCTV.
OL,19,FNeither Brown nor Khaengraeng had made
OL,20,Fa note about the pensioner's fall.
