OL,6,FThey were suspended immediately and an
OL,7,Finvestigation was carried out and it
OL,8,Fwas reported to the police.
OL,10,FBoth carers blamed short staffing and
OL,11,Fa lack of training but admitted they
OL,12,Fshould have put the man "at the top of
OL,13,Fthe list" for urgent help after his
OL,14,Ffall.
OL,16,FBrown, 57, of Hedon, and Khaengraeng,
OL,17,F37, of the New Bridge Road area of
OL,18,Feast Hull, admitted ill-treating a
OL,19,Fperson while working as care workers
OL,20,Fon June 22, 2022.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/11
