OL,6,FRecorder Andrew Latimer said the man
OL,7,Fwas "very vulnerable" and "deserved
OL,8,Fcompassion and respect towards the end
OL,9,Fof his life".
OL,11,F"Both of you saw him and walked past
OL,12,Fhim and left him there for the better
OL,13,Fpart of one hour," said Recorder
OL,14,FLatimer.
OL,16,F"Each of you walked past him several
OL,17,Ftimes, sometimes not even speaking to
OL,18,Fhim, and certainly ignoring his
OL,19,Fplight. That gentleman was distressed.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G9/11
